nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 16
Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 16 is the sixteenth issue of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine. It was released on February 13, 2013.

Prepare yourself for a super smackdown in this issue of Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine as Obi-Wan takes on Pre Vizsla from the Death Watch in the rematch to end all rematches! Which of these great warriors will reign triumphant? Plus, from pits to protocols, we take a look at the greatest droids in the galaxy!
